These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
House: cape-cod, cottage, palace
1. the cottage house is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the palace house and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| House   | cottage     | cape-cod    | palace   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
There 3 different types of food: pepper, artichoke, onion
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person eating onion is between the person eating pepper and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Food     | artichoke | onion | pepper         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, jazz
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is between the owner of the ferret and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | funk     | jazz |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, dancing, chess
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Hobby   | dancing  | chess     | reading |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, roller, quad-bike
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | ship | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking 7up##2
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage   | 7up  | milk   | tea        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, dancing, board-games
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person eating pineapple and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Hobby   | dancing | puzzles | board-games     |

