.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, rock-climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | card-games | dancing  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

