.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, rose
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who growsaconite is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Flower         | rose | aconite | iris |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

