.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
3 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, frog
1. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Pet       | fish  | frog | turtle |

