.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, police-officer, nurse
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the dressmaker##1
2. the nurse is between the dressmaker and the police-officer##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Job         | police-officer | nurse | dressmaker |

