.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, polish
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, board-games, writing
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the mexican and the polish##2
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian   | polish   |
| Hobby         | writing  | collecting | board-games |

