.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, baccarat, bolivar
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking water and the baccarat-smoker##2
3. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | water | tea   | iced-tea |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | cain | baccarat   |

 